data.description: INCREDIBLE INVESTMENT OPPORTUNITY! Grab this LEVEL lot zoned MUR45- near the corner of 147th and Meridian. You can combine with neighboring lot (MLS#2202849) to double your investment to 16,328 sqft of developable space.  That adjacent neighboring lot is on a corner making utility and parking access easy! This location is unbeatable with just a quick walk to future light rail station on 145th, along with the upcoming 145th St corridor improvement projects. Additionally, this home is in GREAT shape so renting while permitting would be a breeze or purchase a a lovely single family home! This thriving community is transitioning to an urban metropolis. What a great time to lock in a coveted piece of the pie!
